# ========================================
# .NET
# ========================================

## Build results
**/bin/
**/obj/

## Windows-style MSBuild/Roslyn BuildHost artifacts created with backslash
## path separators on macOS/Linux (e.g. a directory literally named "bin\Debug").
## gitignore cannot match a literal backslash (it's the escape char), so we
## use ? which matches any single non-/ character including \.
**/bin?Debug
**/bin?Release
**/obj?Debug
**/obj?Release

## User-specific files
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.rsuser

## Build logs
**/*.log
**/msbuild.*.binlog
**/msbuild.*.binlogs

## NuGet
**/project.lock.json
**/project.fragment.lock.json
**/artifacts/

## Visual Studio
.vs/
**/*.userprefs

