**/out/
**/build/
**/dist/

## Debug logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

## Vercel
**/.vercel

## TypeScript
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/next-env.d.ts

## Environment files
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development.local
**/.env.test.local
**/.env.production.local

